channel.title: 317 Mac source?
channel.description:
Hey everyone,
I have been in the Server Downloads section for hours. I cannot seem to find a 317 source for a Mac that has a valid link. Most of the sources have been removed because of legal reasons. Do any of you guys have what I'm looking for? If so, please post a link. Also do not comment saying "Wrong section, look harder" etc. If you don't have what I need, then don't comment at all. Save your self some time, and save me by not making me mad. Thanks guys.
